## 🛠️ Templates Diseñados

### Template 1: Cafe Visit

**Prompts:**
1. Title & one-liner
2. First impressions (arriving, ambiente)
3. The coffee (type, quality, temperature)
4. The atmosphere (lighting, music, people)
5. Notable details (barista, decor)
6. Reflection (why special, memories triggered)
7. Rating (optional 1-5)

**Output structure:**
```markdown
# [Title]

::gallery
![](image1.jpg)
![](image2.jpg)
::

## La Experiencia
[Texto prompt 2]

## El Café
[Texto prompts 3-5]

## Reflexión
[Texto prompt 6]

---
⭐ [Rating]/5
```

### Template 2: Food Experience

**Prompts:**
1. Title & dish name
2. The arrival (presentation)
3. The taste (flavors, textures)
4. The context (who with, why here)
5. Standout moments
6. Would you return?

### Template 3: City Exploration

**Prompts:**
1. Title & route/area
2. Starting point & mood
3. Discoveries along the way
4. Best moment/photo
5. Reflections while walking
6. New perspectives gained

### Template 4: Travel Story

**Prompts:**
1. Title & destination
2. Journey there (anticipation, arrival)
3. Key moments (chronological or highlights)
4. People encountered
5. Unexpected moments
6. Takeaway (what stays with you)

### Template 5: Free Form

**Prompts:**
1. Title
2. Opening thought
3. Main narrative (single text area)
4. Closing reflection

