- Visualize connections between posts
- Link cafés → neighborhoods → trips
- Tag-based clustering
- Interactive exploration

### Built-in Search
- Full-text search
- Tag filtering
- Date range
- Location filtering

### Backlinks
- See related posts automatically
- "Mentioned in: [other posts]"
- Wiki-style navigation

### Gallery Support
```markdown
::gallery
![Caption](image1.jpg)
![Caption](image2.jpg)
::
```

Renders as masonry grid with lightbox.

